# ── Environment files (CRITICAL: never commit real secrets) ──────────────
# Only .env.example is tracked — it contains placeholder values for documentation.
# All other .env* files contain real secrets (DB passwords, API keys, VAPID keys,
# encryption keys) and MUST NOT be committed to version control.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
